  69      """C{Table} is used for representing data or components in a 
  70      pageable and selectable table. 
  71   
  72      Scalability of the Table is largely dictated by the container. A table 
  73      does not have a limit for the number of items and is just as fast with 
  74      hundreds of thousands of items as with just a few. The current GWT 
  75      implementation with scrolling however limits the number of rows to 
  76      around 500000, depending on the browser and the pixel height of rows. 
  77
